FEATURES:

   -it plays!
   -prev/next/stop/pause work.
   -playlist editor with add/remove/clear/all/randomize.
   -shows id3 tags (if present)
   -file filtering for *.mp3 (case insensitive).
   -passing start directory on command line seems to be working.
   -GAMPDIR environmental vairiable can be used to specify start directory.
   -can edit playlist while playing
   -toggle spectrum display on/off
   -toggle between time elapsed/remaining
